<title>subjectRelTable</title>
<shortdesc>Specifies structured associations between subjects.</shortdesc><?Pub Caret1?>
<refbody>
<section><title>Description</title><p>The <keyword>subjectRelTable</keyword> element
provides a tabular structure for associating subjects as an alternative to
the <xref href="relatedSubjects.xml" type="reference"></xref> element. Each
row in the table specifies an association between subjects where the columns
of the table indicate a role for the members of the association. See also <xref
format="html" href="http://www.ontopia.net/topicmaps/materials/tao.html#d0e893">http://www.ontopia.net/topicmaps/materials/tao.html#d0e893</xref>.</p
></section>
